88
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, I'm Asa's aunt, Koudai.</i></font>

89
00:06:32,370 --> 00:06:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I missed your calls.</font>

90
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No worries. Is Asa-san okay?</i></font>

91
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that's the thing...</font>

92
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She left like she always does
both yesterday and today,</font>

93
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I assumed she was in school.</font>

94
00:06:48,250 --> 00:06:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That makes sense.</font>

95
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did she come home like always too?</font>

96
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:55,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, she did yesterday.</font>

97
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the evening, at the same time as usual.</font>

98
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I do...?</font>

99
