<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right.</font>

100
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:04,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll figure it out.</font>

101
00:07:05,030 --> 00:07:08,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Both Asa and I are chicken,</font>

102
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we've never skipped school 
or anything like that.</font>

103
00:07:11,570 --> 00:07:15,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I think there must be a reason.</i></font>

104
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I doubt she's doing anything reckless.</i></font>

105
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:21,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Though I'm kinda bummed 
she lied to me too...</i></font>

106
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. Thank you.</font>

107
00:07:25,970 --> 00:07:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Emiri-san?</font>

108
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah?</i></font>

109
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:31,170
