112
00:07:38,330 --> 00:07:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm worried about her.</font>

113
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't just sit around and wait.</font>

114
