115
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sorry. Can you message me later?</i></font>

116
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sensei, I apologize for the trouble.</i></font>

117
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

118
00:07:51,370 --> 00:07:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have our meeting soon, 
so let's talk then.</font>

119
00:07:54,370 --> 00:07:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes, of course. Please excuse me.</i></font>

