<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah.</font>

124
00:08:08,150 --> 00:08:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you happen to know what 
her late parents were like?</font>

125
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, uh...</font>

126
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her mom was super organized.</font>

127
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And her dad barely ever spoke.</font>

128
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm not too sure.</font>

129
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:30,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lately, I've realized that I don't 
 know what people are truly like.</font>

130
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's very mature of you.</font>

